		   <table class="mform"  border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">The Warrior Epic Stages<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: The Warrior Epic Stages";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Thu, Oct 4th 10:04 PM2001 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/db/classes.html?class=1&mid=100224749898280&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=1&mid=100224749898280&post=1&replyto=100224749898280"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=100224749898280></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=103857"><span id=>FenVen</span></a><b><span id=></span></b><br />41 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Good [3.75]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=FenVen&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>here is the steps you have to do in order to get the elusive epic =)<br><br><br>Quest Start<br>Talk to Kargek Redblade and Wenden in East Freeport to start the quest.<br>Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt<br><br>1, Go to Lake Rathetear. Swim to the Flame Tower Island, then swim underwater and find the tunnel going underneath the island. <br>Pick up the Unjeweled Dragon Head Hilt. <br>2, Obtain a Diamond, Black Sapphire and Jacinth. <br>3, Give the Unjeweled Dragon Head Hilt, Diamond, Black Sapphire and Jacinth to Wenden to get the Jeweled Dragon Head Hilt. <br>Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt<br><br>1, Go to Timorous Deep. Go to the Chessboard Island. <br>2, Pick up the Damaged Dragon Head Hilt that is at the Chessboard. <br>3, Go to Plane of Fear. Kill Fright, Dread or Terror to get the Ball of Everliving Golem. <br>4, Go to Dreadlands. Kill all the giants at the castle until the Mountain Giant Patriarch spawns. <br>5, Kill the Mountain Giant Patriarch to get the Giant Monocle. <br>6, Go to Frontier Mountains. Give the Giant Monocle to Mentrax Mountainbone in the giant fort to get the Rejesium Ore. <br>7, Go to East Freeport. Give the Damaged Dragon Head Hilt, Ball of Everliving Golem and Rejesium Ore to Wenden to get the Finely Crafted Dragon Head Hilt. <br>Ancient Sword Blade [First]<br><br>1, Go to Ocean of Tears. Talk to Denken Strongpick and he tells you the items he wants. <br>2, Go to almost any merchant selling alcoholic beverages to buy a Keg of Vox Tail Ale. <br>3, Go to Permafrost. Kill the Ice Giants to get a Block of Perma Frost. <br>4, Obtain two Rebreathers from any player Tinkerer. <br>5, Go to Ocean of Tears. Give the Keg of Vox Tail Ale, Block of Perma Frost and two Rebreathers to Denken Strongpick to get the Ancient Sword Blade. <br>Ancient Sword Blade [Second]<br><br>1, Go to Chardok. Kill the queen to get the Ancient Sword Blade. <br>The Red Scabbard<br><br>1, Go to East Freeport. Talk to Kargak Redblade. Say "I will do you a favor" to get the letter. <br>2, Go to The Ferrott. Give the letter to Oknoggin to get the Tiny Lute. <br>3, Go to East Freeport. Give the Tiny Lute to Kargak Redblade to get the book. <br>4, Go to Highpass Hold. Give the book to Tenal Redblade to get the Frozen War Totem. <br>5, Go to Permafrost. Kill the Goblin Wizards to get the Frozen Goblin Heart. <br>6, Go to Highpass Hold. Give the Frozen War Totem and Frozen Goblin Heart to Tenal Redblade to get the Totem of Fiery War. <br>7, Go to Emerald Jungle. Kill Severlious to get the Green Dragon Scale. <br>8, Kill either Nagafin [SolB,] Ragefire [SolB,] or Talendor [Skyfire] to get the Red Dragon Scale. <br>9, Go to Highpass Hold. Give the Totem of Fiery War, Green Dragon Scale and Red Dragon Scale to Tenal Redblade to get the Mark of the Sword. <br>10, Go to Plane of Hate. Kill Hand of maestro to get The hand of the maestro. <br>11, Go to Highpass Hold. Give the Mark of the Sword and Maestro's hand to Tenal Redblade to get another note. <br>12, Go to Plane of Sky. Kill the Spiroc Lord to get the Spiroc Wingblade. <br>13, Go to East Freeport. Give the note and Spiroc Wingblade to Kargek Redblade to get the Red Scabbard, along with instuctions on how to combine the swords.<br><br><br><br>well i hope this helped you at least a little bit, =) Good Luck To you<br><br>Fenily Venily<br>Member of the "Knights of Loyalty" guild<br>Cazic Thule Server<br>44th lvl warrior (soon to be 45)&nbsp;&nbsp; =)</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >0 Replies</td></tr></table>
